---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Cool Name Maker | Generate Creative Names" description="Privacy Policy for Cool Name Maker - Learn how we protect your data and privacy when using our name generation tools">
    <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
        <h1 class="text-3xl text-center font-bold mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
        
        <div class="prose max-w-none">
    

            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Introduction</h2>
                <p>Welcome to Cool Name Maker. We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This privacy policy explains how we handle any information collected when you visit coolnamemaker.com.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>
                <p>We collect minimal information to improve your experience:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4">
                    <li>Usage data through analytics to understand how visitors interact with our site</li>
                    <li>Any names you generate are processed locally and not stored on our servers</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">How We Use Your Information</h2>
                <p>The information we collect is used to:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4">
                    <li>Improve our name generation algorithms</li>
                    <li>Enhance website functionality and user experience</li>
                    <li>Analyze site traffic and usage patterns</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Cookies</h2>
                <p>We use essential cookies to ensure the basic functionality of our website. These cookies do not track personal information.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Third-Party Services</h2>
                <p>We may use third-party services for analytics and site improvement. These services may collect anonymous usage data subject to their own privacy policies.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Data Security</h2>
                <p>We implement appropriate security measures to protect your information. Name generation occurs in your browser, and we don't store or transmit your generated names.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
                <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify users of any material changes by posting the new policy on this page.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
                <p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us through our website.</p>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>
